"NOWPayments a ṱuṱuwedza u ṱolea ṱolwila ḓivho ra vhathu vha ṅwalwa kha "
"crypto wallet. Vhoṱhe vhathu vha ḓiṱoḓi a ṱeḓa kha wallet – u no vha munu "
"wuvha."

