msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Mavhisi a Stripe Crypto (USDC) a vha na uṱo na vhuṱanzi nga tshifhinga tsha "
"US. Nga uri u ndi nga tshifhinga tsha US, Stripe a a ṱoḓa u khwaṱwa dza card"
" dza ḓiṱhomo kha stripe balance ḽi (nga u khwinza uḽa crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Nga uri ndi nga US, u nga shumisa Stripe u wana crypto nga u khwinza. Nga "
"uri ndi nga tshifhinga tsha US, ṱiḓisa NOWPayments kana CoinGate u wana "
"crypto nga u khwinza."

