msgid ""
"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments i fanela uri u nga humbela mishumo ya khridi card zwavhudza "
"vhukhu wa crypto u nga vhuywa."

